 hi MatchParen    ctermbg=NONE                    ctermfg=<%=  yellow[2] %>       guibg=NONE                    guifg=<%=  yellow[1] %>       cterm=NONE       gui=NONE

 hi SpellBad      ctermbg=NONE                    ctermfg=<%=  red[2] %>          guibg=NONE                    guifg=NONE                    cterm=undercurl  gui=undercurl  guisp=<%= red[1] %>
 hi SpellCap      ctermbg=NONE                    ctermfg=<%=  light_aqua[2] %>   guibg=NONE                    guifg=NONE                    cterm=undercurl  gui=undercurl  guisp=<%= light_aqua[1] %>
